name: Club Stands
description:
If you would like your club represented at the show please get in touch with the team who can book you a spot at the show. 

Space is limited so please book early to avoid disappointment! 

Closing date for booking club stands is the July 23rd 2012.

Club Stand Driver and Passenger Tickets - £6.00 Each

You will still need to post us a booking form!

name: Public Entry Ticket
description:
Tickets cost £7.00 which will admit one adult entry into the show. Under 12’s go free as long as they are accompanied by a paying adult, with a maximum of 2 children per one paying adult. 

Every ticket purchased on the day of the show we will donate £1.00 To Cancer Research.

Cancer Research UK is the world's leading charity dedicated to beating cancer through research. Thanks to there groundbreaking work more people are beating cancer than ever before.

View their website to find out more - Follow them on Facebook - www.facebook.com/cancerresearchuk
